output_list.criticism: The contract has an integer overflow vulnerability in the if condition. The value of entry_number is incremented by 1 in each transaction, but it is not checked whether it exceeds the maximum value that can be stored in a uint256 variable. This can lead to an overflow, which can result in incorrect results and potentially loss of funds.
